description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a full time (37.5 hours/week) Band 5 Registered Nurse for our busy and thriving Outpatients departments at William Harvey Hospital and Royal Victoria Hospital, Folkestone, part of East Kent Hospitals University NHS Foundation Trust. The post will involve working between both sites and working at weekends on a rotational basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outpatient services are growing and there has never been a better time to join our team and develop your nursing career. We are looking for a friendly and dynamic individual with excellent communication skills to help ensure the delivery of a high quality, evidence based and cost effective Outpatient service for patients and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must be enthusiastic, demonstrate effective interpersonal skills and be able to work autonomously as well as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The department is both challenging and rewarding. As part of your role you will also be involved in helping to develop the HCA’s who play an important role within the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We aim to provide safe and effective care that exceeds the expectations of our patients and the public and we are&lt;strong&gt; looking for excellent nurses who embrace our Trust values and care so that:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People feel &lt;strong&gt;cared&lt;/strong&gt; for as individuals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People feel &lt;strong&gt;safe&lt;/strong&gt;, reassured and involved&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People feel that we are &lt;strong&gt;making a difference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People feel teamwork, trust and &lt;strong&gt;respect&lt;/strong&gt; sit at the heart of everything we do&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
